                      Winter bazaar                    The name says it all. Fashion, food, fun, music et al, Winter Wows is an exhibition of latest trends in fashion and lifestyle, hosted just in time to bring on the Christmas fever. Megha Agarwal, Garima Agarwal and Ritika Bose Gurbani, the organisers of this event, also aim to create a unique experience for people at the onset of the party season. Keeping the wintery weather in mind, the venue and the outdoor ambience is being done up with tents and kiosks, with live music and food for entertainment  what more can one ask for! The event will serve as a platform for undiscovered talents of the city who will showcase art, apparel, maternity wear, furnishings, accessories, lifestyle, health and wellness products, as well as sinful desserts to binge on. Upcoming Delhi-based designer brand Cranberry with the latest in ladies fashion, Hopskotch to entice moms with home-linen for children, wellness, health and spa products by Mumbai-based brand Loose Ends, Pashminas and Jamewar stoles and shawls straight from Kashmir and several more will make you want to burn a hole in your pocket!                  lEvent: An exhibition of winter fashion and lifestyle products lWhen: Today; 11 am - 9 pm lWhere: Solace Spa lawns, Sunny Park	                    
